This reaction was recognized by its great success and high efficiency to remove many organic and inorganic recalcitrant compounds from soil and water (Telles and Granhen Tavares 2012; Nidheesh et al. 2013; Yue et al. 2015; Martínez-Costa et al. 2018; Giraldo-Aguirre et al. 2018; Verma and Chaudhari 2020). This is due to the intensive oxidative power, short lifetime, and high reactivity of the ·OH\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
